---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact" description="Get in touch with PetCare.Software. Start your free trial, request a demo, or get support for your pet care management software.">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-navy to-gray-900 text-white py-16">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="badge-primary mb-4">Contact</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Get in Touch</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">
          Ready to streamline your pet care business? Start your free trial or reach out with any questions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">Contact Information</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="card">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Support</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Need help with your account or have a technical question?
              </p>
              <a href="mailto:help@petcare.software" class="link mt-2 inline-block">
                help@petcare.software
              </a>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">General Inquiries</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Questions about pricing, features, or partnerships?
              </p>
              <a href="mailto:info@petcare.software" class="link mt-2 inline-block">
                info@petcare.software
              </a>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Company Address</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                LEAVE.REVIEW LTD<br />
                124 City Road<br />
                London, England<br />
                EC1V 2NX
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card bg-gray-50">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">Start Your Free Trial</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Fill out the form below and we'll get you set up with a 14-day free trial. No credit card required.
          </p>
          <form class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Your Name</label>
              <input type="text" id="name" name="name" class="input" required />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Email Address</label>
              <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="input" required />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="business" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Business Name</label>
              <input type="text" id="business" name="business" class="input" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="type" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Business Type</label>
              <select id="type" name="type" class="input">
                <option value="">Select your business type</option>
                <option value="daycare">Dog Daycare</option>
                <option value="boarding">Dog Boarding / Kennel</option>
                <option value="cattery">Cattery</option>
                <option value="mixed">Mixed Facility</option>
                <option value="other">Other</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Message (Optional)</label>
              <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" class="input"></textarea>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn-primary w-full justify-center">
              Start Free Trial
            </button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy text-center mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">What is PetCare.Software?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">An all-in-one platform for bookings, payments, and operations across dog daycare, cattery, kennel, and grooming.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">How does it save time?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">It automates booking, capacity management, reminders, and invoicing to cut manual admin.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Does it support multiple locations?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Yes, you can manage multi-location calendars and roles from one dashboard.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Can I migrate from spreadsheets?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Yes â€” import tools and guided onboarding make switching straightforward.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
